label: PDP | Accordions
description:
Built the accordions in a new way which allows more flexibility in content element order.

Each accordion is represented as its own tile making use of a single "base accordion" tile. The base accordion tile allows us to control the spacing and maximum height of a single accordion.

New content elements can be added by adding variants to the "Accordion content" element.

Let me know what you think.
